# Friendly URL on any host: /dispatch-live → dispatch-live.html
# Note: a previous attempt at host-conditional routing
# (`/* /dispatch-live.html 200! Host=dispatch.jobsiteexchange.com`)
# was removed in 2026-05-29 because Netlify _redirects does NOT support
# Host= as a conditional. The dispatch.* hostname is now routed by a
# synchronous head-script at the top of driver.html (index.html) which
# does location.replace('/dispatch-live.html') when location.hostname
# starts with 'dispatch.'.
/dispatch-live  /dispatch-live.html  200
